---

**Qaysi index — qanday log:**

| Pipeline | ES Index | Interval | Nima keladi |
|----------|----------|----------|-------------|
| 01_discovery | `metrics-snmp.discovery` | 1 soat | `vendor`, `interface_count`, `device.name/location` — qurilma pasporti |
| 02_critical | `metrics-snmp.critical` | 60s | Har interface uchun alohida: `interface.oper_status`, `device.cpu.util_pct` |
| 03_normal | `metrics-snmp.bandwidth` | 5 daqiqa | Har interface: `interface.in_bytes`, `out_bytes`, xatoliklar |
| 04_inventory | `metrics-snmp.inventory` | 6 soat | `device.serial_number`, `device.firmware`, `device.model` |
| 05_trap | `logs-snmp.trap` | Real-time | `event.action`, `interface.name`, trap sababi |

**Rule yozganda:**
- Port o'chdi/yondi → `logs-snmp.trap` (darhol) + `metrics-snmp.critical` (60s backup)
- Bandwidth yuqori → `metrics-snmp.bandwidth`
- Qurilma reboot → `logs-snmp.trap` (`event.action: device-coldstart`)

**Yangi switch qo'shganda** — faqat `hosts => [...]` ga yangi IP qo'shing + vendor OID regex qo'shing. Boshqa hamma narsa avtomatik ishlaydi.
